 eternal &quot;I&quot; became &quot;we&quot;'</a></p> <p>• <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/oct/17/morrissey-auobiography-10-things-we-learned\">Morrissey: 10 things we learned from Autobiography</a></p> <p>He's since gone home for a well-earned rest – and, meanwhile, here's how the rest of Twitter has been getting on:</p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/garyjkemp/statuses/390735044517441536\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Got it. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23morrissey&amp;src=hash\">#morrissey</a>. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23penguinclassic&amp;src=hash\">#penguinclassic</a> <a href=\"http://t.co/aNrORtEtT7\">pic.twitter.com/aNrORtEtT7</a></p>— Gary Kemp (@garyjkemp) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/garyjkemp/statuses/390735044517441536\">October 17, 2013</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/amylame/statuses/390775659834138624\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Got it!!! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23morrissey&amp;src=hash\">#morrissey</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23autobiography&amp;src=hash\">#autobiography</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Foyles\">@foyles</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PenguinUKBooks\">@PenguinUKBooks</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23mozarmy&amp;src=hash\">#mozarmy</a> <a href=\"http://t.co/0nht935sDP\">pic.twitter.com/0nht935sDP</a></p>— amy lam&eacute; (@amylame) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/amylame/statuses/390775659834138624\">October 17, 2013</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/Crash_Records/statuses/390760431457165312\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Early visit to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WaterstoneLeeds\">@WaterstoneLeeds</a> to pick up the Morrissey autobiography. Can't see me doing much work today! <a href=\"http://t.co/0u51ojGlKP\">p